,"code":"SCNText"},{"text":"로 3D 텍스트 지오메트리를 만들고,","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"text":"얼굴 앵커 노드의 자식으로 추가해 얼굴을 따라다니게 합니다.","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"text":"텍스트 생성 코드는 ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"Coordinator"},{"type":"text","text":" 안에 작성합니다."}],"action":{"isActive":true,"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/arhelloface.ARHelloFace\/tutorials\/ARHelloFace\/03-HelloText","overridingTitle":"Get started","overridingTitleInlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Get started"}]},"featuredEyebrow":"Tutorial"}],"metadata":{"role":"project","title":"ARFaceTrackingConfiguration으로 얼굴 인식","categoryPathComponent":"ARHelloFace","category":"ARKit으로 얼굴 인식하기"},"references":{"doc://arhelloface.ARHelloFace/tutorials/ARHelloFace/03-HelloText#%EC%96%BC%EA%B5%B4-%EC%9C%84%EC%97%90-%ED%85%8D%EC%8A%A4%ED%8A%B8-%EC%9C%84%EC%B9%98-%EC%9E%A1%EA%B8%B0":{"kind":"section","type":"section","abstract":[{"text":"이제 얼굴 위에 “Hello” 텍스트를 3D로 표시합니다.","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"SceneKit의 ","type":"text"},{"code":"SCNText","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":"로 3D 텍스트 지오메트리를 만들고,","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"얼굴 앵커 노드의 자식으로 추가해 얼굴을 따라다니게 합니다.","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"텍스트 생성 코드는 ","type":"text"},{"code":"Coordinator","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":" 안에 작성합니다.","type":"text"}],"url":"\/tutorials\/arhelloface\/03-hellotext#%EC%96%BC%EA%B5%B4-%EC%9C%84%EC%97%90-%ED%85%8D%EC%8A%A4%ED%8A%B8-%EC%9C%84%EC%B9%98-%EC%9E%A1%EA%B8%B0","title":"얼굴 위에 텍스트 위치 잡기","role":"pseudoSymbol","identifier":"doc:\/\/arhelloface.ARHelloFace\/tutorials\/ARHelloFace\/03-HelloText#%EC%96%BC%EA%B5%B4-%EC%9C%84%EC%97%90-%ED%85%8D%EC%8A%A4%ED%8A%B8-%EC%9C%84%EC%B9%98-%EC%9E%A1%EA%B8%B0"},"s2-check-support.swift":{"type":"file","syntax":"swift","identifier":"s2-check-support.swift","content":["import SwiftUI","import ARKit","","struct ContentView: View {","    var body: some View {","        \/\/ Face Tracking 지원 여부 확인 (TrueDepth 카메라 필요)","        if ARFaceTrackingConfiguration.isSupported {","            ARFaceView()","                .ignoresSafeArea()","        } else {","            \/\/ 미지원 기기 안내 화면 (UIAlertController 대신 SwiftUI 뷰로 표시)","            VStack(spacing: 12) {","                Image(systemName: \"faceid\")","                    .font(.system(size: 48))","                Text(\"미지원 기기\")","                    .font(.title2).bold()","                Text(\"Face Tracking은 TrueDepth 카메라가 있는\\n기기에서만 동작합니다.\")","                    .multilineTextAlignment(.center)","                    .foregroundStyle(.secondary)","            }","            .padding()","        }","    }","}"],"fileName":"ContentView.swift","highlights":[],"fileType":"swift"},"s2-coordinator-adopt.swift":{"type":"file","syntax":"swift","identifier":"s2-coordinator-adopt.swift","content":["\/\/ s2-coordinator-adopt.swift","import SwiftUI","import ARKit","import SceneKit","","struct ARFaceView: UIViewRepresentable {","","    \/\/ Coordinator를 생성합니다. UIKit의 delegate 역할을 담당합니다.","    func makeCoordinator() -> Coordinator {","        Coordinator()","    }","","    func makeUIView(context: Context) -> ARSCNView {","        let sceneView = ARSCNView()","        sceneView.delegate = context.coordinator  \/\/ delegate 연결","        sceneView.showsStatistics = true","        sceneView.autoenablesDefaultLighting = true","","        let configuration = ARFaceTrackingConfiguration()","        configuration.isLightEstimationEnabled = true","        sceneView.session.run(configuration, options: [.resetTracking, .removeExistingAnchors])","        return sceneView","    }","","    func updateUIView(_ uiView: ARSCNView, context: Context) {}","","    \/\/ ARSCNViewDelegate를 채택하는 Coordinator","    \/\/ SwiftUI 구조체는 delegate가 될 수 없으므로 NSObject 클래스로 분리합니다.","    class Coordinator: NSObject, ARSCNViewDelegate {","    }","}"],"fileName":"ARFaceView.swift","highlights":[],"fileType":"swift"},"doc://arhelloface.ARHelloFace/tutorials/ARHelloFace":{"kind":"overview","title":"ARKit으로 Hello 띄우기","url":"\/tutorials\/arhelloface","abstract":[{"text":"ARKit의 Face Tracking 기능을 활용해 카메라로 사람 얼굴을 인식하고,","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"머리 위에 “Hello” 텍스트를 증강현실로 표시하는 앱을 단계별로 만들어봅니다.","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"SwiftUI 앱에서 "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"UIViewRepresentable"},{"type":"text","text":"로 ARSCNView를 감싸 사용합니다."}],"type":"topic","identifier":"doc:\/\/arhelloface.ARHelloFace\/tutorials\/ARHelloFace","role":"overview"},"doc://arhelloface.ARHelloFace/tutorials/ARHelloFace/02-FaceTracking#Coordinator%EB%A1%9C-%EC%96%BC%EA%B5%B4-%EC%95%B5%EC%BB%A4-%EC%B6%94%EC%A0%81":{"kind":"section","title":"Coordinator로 얼굴 앵커 추적","url":"\/tutorials\/arhelloface\/02-facetracking#Coordinator%EB%A1%9C-%EC%96%BC%EA%B5%B4-%EC%95%B5%EC%BB%A4-%EC%B6%94%EC%A0%81","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"ARKit의 "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"ARFaceTrackingConfiguration"},{"type":"text","text":"을 사용하면"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"TrueDepth 카메라로 실시간 얼굴 위치, 방향, 표정 데이터를 얻을 수 있습니다."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"이 챕터에서는 AR 세션을 시작하고, "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"Coordinator"},{"type":"text","text":"로 "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"ARFaceAnchor"},{"type":"text","text":"를 감지합니다."}],"type":"section","identifier":"doc:\/\/arhelloface.ARHelloFace\/tutorials\/ARHelloFace\/02-FaceTracking#Coordinator%EB%A1%9C-%EC%96%BC%EA%B5%B4-%EC%95%B5%EC%BB%A4-%EC%B6%94%EC%A0%81","role":"pseudoSymbol"},"doc://arhelloface.ARHelloFace/tutorials/ARHelloFace/01-ProjectSetup#Xcode-%ED%94%84%EB%A1%9C%EC%A0%9D%ED%8A%B8-%EC%83%9D%EC%84%B1":{"kind":"section","type":"section","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"ARKit Face Tracking을 사용하려면 TrueDepth 카메라를 지원하는"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"기기(iPhone X 이상)가 필요합니다."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"이 챕터에서는 SwiftUI 프로젝트를 만들고, UIKit 뷰인 "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"ARSCNView"},{"type":"text","text":"를"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"UIViewRepresentable"},{"type":"text","text":"로 감싸 화면에 배치합니다."}],"url":"\/tutorials\/arhelloface\/01-projectsetup#Xcode-%ED%94%84%EB%A1%9C%EC%A0%9D%ED%8A%B8-%EC%83%9D%EC%84%B1","title":"Xcode 프로젝트 생성","role":"pseudoSymbol","identifier":"doc:\/\/arhelloface.ARHelloFace\/tutorials\/ARHelloFace\/01-ProjectSetup#Xcode-%ED%94%84%EB%A1%9C%EC%A0%9D%ED%8A%B8-%EC%83%9D%EC%84%B1"},"s2-pause-session.swift":{"type":"file","syntax":"swift","identifier":"s2-pause-session.swift","content":["\/\/ s2-pause-session.swift","\/\/ 뷰가 화면에서 사라지면 SwiftUI가 ARSCNView를 해제합니다.","\/\/ UIViewRepresentable의 dismantleUIView(_:coordinator:)에서 세션을 정리합니다.","\/\/ (UIKit의 viewWillDisappear에 해당하는 역할)","static func dismantleUIView(_ uiView: ARSCNView, coordinator: Coordinator) {","    \/\/ 화면 이탈 시 AR 세션 일시정지","    uiView.session.pause()","}"],"fileName":"ARFaceView.swift","highlights":[{"line":1},{"line":2},{"line":3},{"line":4},{"line":5},{"line":6},{"line":7}],"fileType":"swift"},"s2-did-update.swift":{"type":"file","syntax":"swift","identifier":"s2-did-update.swift","content":["\/\/ s2-did-update.swift","\/\/ Coordinator 클래스 안에 추가하는 델리게이트 메서드입니다.","\/\/\/ ARKit이 매 프레임마다 앵커 transform을 자동으로 node에 동기화합니다.","\/\/\/ 추가 처리가 필요한 경우 이 메서드에서 구현합니다.","func renderer(_ renderer: SCNSceneRenderer, didUpdate node: SCNNode, for anchor: ARAnchor) {","    guard let faceAnchor = anchor as? ARFaceAnchor else { return }","","    \/\/ faceAnchor.blendShapes로 표정 데이터 접근 가능 (선택적 확장)","    \/\/ 예: let smileLeft = faceAnchor.blendShapes[.mouthSmileLeft]","    _ = faceAnchor  \/\/ 현재는 ARKit이 transform을 자동 처리하므로 추가 작업 불필요","}"],"fileName":"ARFaceView.swift","highlights":[{"line":1},{"line":2},{"line":3},{"line":4},{"line":5},{"line":6},{"line":8},{"line":9},{"line":10}],"fileType":"swift"},"doc://arhelloface.ARHelloFace/tutorials/ARHelloFace/02-FaceTracking":{"kind":"project","type":"topic","abstract":[{"text":"ARKit의 ","type":"text"},{"code":"ARFaceTrackingConfiguration","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":"을 사용하면","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"TrueDepth 카메라로 실시간 얼굴 위치, 방향, 표정 데이터를 얻을 수 있습니다.","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"이 챕터에서는 AR 세션을 시작하고, ","type":"text"},{"code":"Coordinator","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":"로 ","type":"text"},{"code":"ARFaceAnchor","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":"를 감지합니다.","type":"text"}],"url":"\/tutorials\/arhelloface\/02-facetracking","estimatedTime":"15min","title":"ARFaceTrackingConfiguration으로 얼굴 인식","role":"project","identifier":"doc:\/\/arhelloface.ARHelloFace\/tutorials\/ARHelloFace\/02-FaceTracking"},"s2-run-session.swift":{"type":"file","syntax":"swift","identifier":"s2-run-session.swift","content":["import SwiftUI","import ARKit","import SceneKit","","struct ARFaceView: UIViewRepresentable {","","    func makeUIView(context: Context) -> ARSCNView {","        let sceneView = ARSCNView()","        sceneView.showsStatistics = true","        sceneView.autoenablesDefaultLighting = true","","        \/\/ ARFaceTrackingConfiguration 생성 및 세션 시작","        let configuration = ARFaceTrackingConfiguration()","        configuration.isLightEstimationEnabled = true","        sceneView.session.run(configuration, options: [.resetTracking, .removeExistingAnchors])","","        return sceneView","    }","","    func updateUIView(_ uiView: ARSCNView, context: Context) {}","}"],"fileName":"ARFaceView.swift","highlights":[],"fileType":"swift"},"doc://arhelloface.ARHelloFace/tutorials/ARHelloFace/01-ProjectSetup":{"kind":"project","title":"프로젝트 설정 및 ARSCNView를 SwiftUI로 감싸기","type":"topic","url":"\/tutorials\/arhelloface\/01-projectsetup","abstract":[{"text":"ARKit Face Tracking을 사용하려면 TrueDepth 카메라를 지원하는","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"기기(iPhone X 이상)가 필요합니다.","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"이 챕터에서는 SwiftUI 프로젝트를 만들고, UIKit 뷰인 ","type":"text"},{"code":"ARSCNView","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":"를","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"code":"UIViewRepresentable","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":"로 감싸 화면에 배치합니다.","type":"text"}],"estimatedTime":"10min","identifier":"doc:\/\/arhelloface.ARHelloFace\/tutorials\/ARHelloFace\/01-ProjectSetup","role":"project"},"s2-node-for-anchor.swift":{"type":"file","syntax":"swift","identifier":"s2-node-for-anchor.swift","content":["import SwiftUI","import ARKit","import SceneKit","","struct ARFaceView: UIViewRepresentable {","","    func makeCoordinator() -> Coordinator {","        Coordinator()","    }","","    func makeUIView(context: Context) -> ARSCNView {","        let sceneView = ARSCNView()","        sceneView.delegate = context.coordinator","        sceneView.showsStatistics = true","        sceneView.autoenablesDefaultLighting = true","","        let configuration = ARFaceTrackingConfiguration()","        configuration.isLightEstimationEnabled = true","        sceneView.session.run(configuration, options: [.resetTracking, .removeExistingAnchors])","        return sceneView","    }","","    func updateUIView(_ uiView: ARSCNView, context: Context) {}","","    static func dismantleUIView(_ uiView: ARSCNView, coordinator: Coordinator) {","        uiView.session.pause()","    }","","    \/\/ MARK: - Coordinator (ARSCNViewDelegate)","","    class Coordinator: NSObject, ARSCNViewDelegate {","","        \/\/\/ 새 앵커가 감지될 때 호출 - ARFaceAnchor이면 노드를 생성해 반환","        func renderer(_ renderer: SCNSceneRenderer, nodeFor anchor: ARAnchor) -> SCNNode? {","            guard anchor is ARFaceAnchor else { return nil }","","            let faceNode = SCNNode()","            \/\/ 다음 챕터에서 이 노드에 \"Hello\" 텍스트를 추가합니다","            return faceNode","        }","    }","}"],"fileName":"ARFaceView.swift","highlights":[{"line":13},{"line":25},{"line":26},{"line":27},{"line":28},{"line":29},{"line":30},{"line":32},{"line":33},{"line":34},{"line":35},{"line":36},{"line":37},{"line":38},{"line":39},{"line":40}],"fileType":"swift"},"doc://arhelloface.ARHelloFace/tutorials/ARHelloFace/03-HelloText#